\section{Discussion}

\begin{frame}{Discussion}
\begin{itemize}
    \item NDVI analysis suggests that the \textbf{vegetation is in a better condition than before}.
    \item Moreover, FCOVER analysis support the evidence since it appears to be increased from 2020 to 2023.
\end{itemize}
\end{frame}

